  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Clinical features, optical coherence tomography findings and surgical outcome in eyes with
      macular retinoschisis and detachment with normal tension glaucoma but without optic disc pit
      or high myopia were evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
